{"tid":878840,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IPhone XR 竟然完全沒有官方保護殼產品","createTime":"2018-10-27T12:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T18:48:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"beb614f383c3feaf7b5f41cf6c9f9660d0d35add","tid":878840,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"藍骨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Screen_Shot_2018_10_26_at_1.44.32_PM.png-694x422.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FScreen_Shot_2018_10_26_at_1.44.32_PM.png-694x422.jpeg&h=091aaa90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直以來 Apple 每次推出新 iPhone，都會有一系列的官方保護殼一併發售，雖然售價比副廠的貴不少，不過也仍然有一定市場。最近 iPhone XR 推出之後，Apple 竟然完全沒有推出任何的保護殼，在官方商店中也只有其他品牌的產品供選購。<br />\n<br />\n雖然之前有消息指 Apple 會推出透明保護殼，讓 iPhone XR 的多種顏色選擇可以更加突出，不過結果而言直至今日為止，在 Apple 的官方商店中，都沒有任何的官方保護殼產品出現。而 iPhone XS 系列則有矽膠殼以及皮製保護殼等多款選擇。當年 iPhone 5C 推出的時候，Apple 更是隆重其事的推出過穿孔設計的矽膠保護殼，帶來不同的色彩配搭效果，今次極低調的做法則令人詫異。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/18zqzthv28x5fjpg-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F18zqzthv28x5fjpg-694x390.jpg&h=4fc3b202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖說目前已經有不少的副廠保護殼可以選擇，不過如果想要選購官方保護殼的話，可能就要失望了。Apple 方面未公佈未來會否推出官方保護殼，不過這樣的產品看來也不似會有生產方面的難題導致延遲推出，因此也很有可能以後都不會有 iPhone XR 官方保護殼。"},{"pid":"15fdde2642c28d165334b83c1bb1ae18f572a6f5","tid":878840,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:39:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/10/27/apple-no-iphone-xr-cases-first-party/mobile-phone/phone-parts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2Fapple-no-iphone-xr-cases-first-party%2Fmobile-phone%2Fphone-parts%2F&d=BBMsXovDUggW2io7Z2ScBcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=534f163b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/10/27/apple-no-iphone-xr-cases-first-party/mobile-phone/phone-parts/</a>"},{"pid":"9cf89bb843e870fc11d163ab65d6d4554021c30e","tid":878840,"uid":182286,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72aed86b2af84f6d353b7c826ba8b640739f4888","tid":878840,"uid":21488,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:42:04.000Z","msg":"個CASE有無得分期"},{"pid":"8d1ed492febdf6a807c84e1a08c2f7a198c7ebcd","tid":878840,"uid":609,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf89bb843e870fc11d163ab65d6d4554021c30e","tid":878840,"uid":182286,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"你真係好落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n瞻你個個xs max post都入去吹奏 個個xr post都入去踩 為乜呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c634560676f0ad9670db656cd2dc7abc79d5643","tid":878840,"uid":7452,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/204203_fba83a584b1970ac94046041068b586a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F204203_fba83a584b1970ac94046041068b586a.png&h=bad28ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/204210_8e9e9a2fdd62fd8865ef95d11d06330b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F204210_8e9e9a2fdd62fd8865ef95d11d06330b.png&h=f442d353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶套搞到條邊更加粗更加柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\"